VFP (file format)
=================

Description
-----------

The .VFP files are used for [Vertex\_and\_fragment\_programs.html material special effects]. They are regular ASCII text files written in assembler which are parsed and compiled by the engine and OpenGL driver and executed on each pixel/vertex.

